{
  "texts": [
    "We directly compare AutoCodeRover with Swe-agent's original results as it is publicly available at GitHub 3.",
    "In contrast to Swe-agent, we do not have access to Devin, so we take the most relevant reported result from their technical report [40].",
    "To avoid the natural randomness of LLM, we repeat our experiments three times.",
    "We report the result with the AutoCodeRover @1 and AutoCodeRover @3 annotations (i.e.",
    "pass@1, pass@3 metrics [8] respectively)."
  ]
}